Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--HALF--
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.00,0:01:41.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.44,0:01:45.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to live...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.07,0:01:49.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.33,0:02:19.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Elen...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.13,0:02:20.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.39,0:02:34.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It has begun, Mr. Shiga.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.49,0:02:37.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is what I've been searching for.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.25,0:02:43.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The play you've written will definitely backfire on you one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.26,0:02:47.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you'll go to hell, Scythe Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.42,0:02:50.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That sounds rather interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.30,0:02:57.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, my fellow creations,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.46,0:03:00.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,sing and dance...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.62,0:03:06.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...in this murderous and blood-thirsty world!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.99,0:03:58.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are these girls?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.65,0:04:02.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no one else in this world with such twisted tastes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.90,0:04:05.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So they're the same as us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.73,0:04:08.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are at least two more of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.95,0:04:10.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.51,0:04:11.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.76,0:04:17.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Apart from these girls, there shouldn't be any more assassins from Inferno.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.67,0:04:20.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.76,0:04:25.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That person won't allow unrefined stage props to appear on the stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.00,0:04:29.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He plans to draw the curtains himself?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.92,0:04:33.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the final battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.50,0:04:44.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Neun and Fünf left the stage?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.52,0:04:47.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're putting up quite a fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.23,0:04:50.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This wasn't part of my scenario.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.53,0:04:51.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.56,0:04:54.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There isn't a better ending scene than this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.06,0:05:02.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.73,0:05:04.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll bait them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.74,0:05:08.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Use this chance to find Scythe.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.53,0:05:11.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The rest will be easy after killing their commander.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.94,0:05:15.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the only one who can understand his intentions.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.90,0:05:21.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.39,0:05:22.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.08,0:05:44.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,2 on 1.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.55,0:05:52.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.62,0:05:56.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're here...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.74,0:06:07.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ein.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.37,0:06:14.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome to my stage!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.25,0:06:33.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't act on your stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.76,0:06:46.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only two are here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.08,0:06:49.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me the others are...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.88,0:06:59.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to surrender?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.56,0:07:03.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm here to kill you...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.52,0:07:04.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.79,0:07:07.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kill me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.67,0:07:10.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.70,0:07:16.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How are you going to kill me when you're on the verge of despair?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.16,0:07:22.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way I'm scheduled to die in this scene of your play.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.59,0:07:27.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You do not wish to see such a boring ending.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.24,0:07:33.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought you would've understood so well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.67,0:07:36.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just as you said.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.63,0:07:44.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The reason why I returned to this island-country is to see the co-acting of my daughters.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.90,0:07:47.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me introduce you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.45,0:07:48.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These two are Sechs and Sieben.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.52,0:07:53.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can acknowledge them as your younger sisters, Ein.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.45,0:07:58.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Ein, your prototype.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.66,0:08:00.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have a little fun with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.39,0:08:03.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And when she reaches her limit,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.58,0:08:06.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,slowly skin her and scrape her flesh off.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.01,0:08:37.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Ein?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.63,0:08:39.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't step back anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.49,0:08:43.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though I went easy on you, you can't even fight back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.85,0:08:44.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.30,0:09:25.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Their thoughts, actions and even breathing...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.98,0:09:32.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...are exactly the same as how you trained me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.58,0:09:36.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.28,0:09:39.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since the moment you created me,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.38,0:09:45.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,nothing has changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.16,0:11:16.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Relying on you even till the end...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.52,0:11:20.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Cal.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.36,0:11:38.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My, my.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.96,0:11:41.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is surprising.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.86,0:11:45.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought you would have such fighting strength in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.35,0:11:47.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you already.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.82,0:11:51.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm here to kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.96,0:11:54.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's impossible for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.45,0:11:55.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.33,0:11:58.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I surrender.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.36,0:12:06.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.73,0:12:11.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That means I'm not a threat to you anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.44,0:12:16.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So? Can you still kill me, Ein?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.92,0:12:22.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the difference between you and Zwei.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.52,0:12:25.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Compared to Zwei who can kill under his own intentions,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.66,0:12:30.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you can only kill under orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.47,0:12:34.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you go against that, your heart will sink to darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.28,0:12:38.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The horror and guilt of killing will swallow you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.70,0:12:45.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your will-less mentality is even weaker than that of a normal person.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.28,0:12:52.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't be able to shoot me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.15,0:12:54.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, it's impossible for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.12,0:13:01.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because... you need me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.80,0:13:09.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for bringing me such an enjoyable night, Ein.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.21,0:13:14.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Elen...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.95,0:13:21.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really are a foolish person.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.31,0:13:26.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you really think you can see through everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.92,0:13:29.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.08,0:13:32.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.79,0:13:33.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.99,0:13:35.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.00,0:13:45.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never forgive you for hurting him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.44,0:13:48.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What will come of killing me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.75,0:13:50.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Others will come and kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.69,0:13:52.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't find your memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.18,0:13:56.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're just walking in a spiral with no end.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.63,0:13:58.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if that's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.11,0:14:03.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can kill you right now, Scythe Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.11,0:14:05.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Beautiful...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.87,0:14:08.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's beautiful, Ein!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.12,0:14:12.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't call me Ein.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.50,0:14:14.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Elen.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.52,0:14:18.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will live the life that he wished for.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.21,0:14:21.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Elen...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.05,0:14:57.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a prank by the Muses.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.78,0:15:28.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please go to hell first.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.51,0:15:34.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I still want to stay with him for a little longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.53,0:16:13.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Elen.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.51,0:16:19.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.02,0:16:22.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So Scythe Master and the Phantoms...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.08,0:16:24.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How should we deal with it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.20,0:16:31.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those who destroy old systems and create new ones are the young ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.21,0:16:35.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Flowers that fade away... Ghosts that don't exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.47,0:16:39.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it's just a fleeting dream,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.03,0:16:44.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we have things we must do.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.66,0:16:52.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.59,0:16:55.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seems like something happened at the chapel and the old school building.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.87,0:16:57.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How scary...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.13,0:17:11.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have a safe trip,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.04,0:17:14.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reiji.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.42,0:17:23.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Helmut von Giuseppe. Born in Berlin.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.98,0:17:29.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doctoral degree in psychology and brain physiology.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.51,0:17:33.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Active as an expert in the fields of interrogation and brainwashing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.57,0:17:37.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After that, he entered the underworld and wandered from place to place.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.29,0:17:40.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He then became the middleman for freelance assassins.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.54,0:17:45.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His nickname in the underworld was Scythe Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.54,0:17:52.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to search for Elen's past, we must research that man's background.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.29,0:17:57.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She met Scythe and began her life as Ein,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.97,0:17:59.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,five years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.48,0:18:05.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Their encounter took place in Hong Kong.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.37,0:18:07.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.06,0:18:10.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This man came to this orphanage?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.50,0:18:14.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, around five years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.24,0:18:18.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He said he wanted to adopt a girl from Ulan Bator.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.66,0:18:22.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Adopt a girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.63,0:18:24.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She was a girl with milky white skin.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.75,0:18:28.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If she's still alive, she'd probably be the same age as you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.63,0:18:32.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This might be my imagination...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.40,0:18:35.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the girl over there looks exactly like her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.87,0:18:39.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ulan Bator.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.54,0:18:41.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We came to Mongolia.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.92,0:18:44.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But we couldn't find any more clues.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.27,0:18:49.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go to the grasslands and look up to the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.57,0:18:52.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll definitely find out that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.64,0:18:55.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as you look up, you will understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.01,0:19:05.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.90,0:19:40.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you are a child of Mongolia, you will never forget the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.01,0:19:46.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sky and the clouds will be engraved into your flesh and bones.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.70,0:19:49.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as you look up, you will understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.41,0:20:00.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think we need to go on anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.12,0:20:02.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.46,0:20:05.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.85,0:20:09.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I remember this sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.65,0:20:12.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've seen it countless times in my dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.38,0:20:15.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seeing this is enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.19,0:20:41.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In my wrongful life where I couldn't fulfill any promises,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.29,0:20:44.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there is still a promise I want to fulfill.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.56,0:20:47.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need to search for my memories anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.24,0:20:55.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I can't find them, I already have the name you gave me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.77,0:20:59.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is to make you smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.06,0:21:07.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have memories of being with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.97,0:21:10.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To find your true smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.46,0:21:15.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One day, I will...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.65,0:21:37.02,Default-M,,0000,0000,0000,,These memories... These memories are enough for me to continue living.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.57,0:21:41.69,Default-M,,0000,0000,0000,,These memories are enough for me.
